---
title: Double Sri Lankan Smooth Dory & Cauliflower Curry with Garlic Rice & Coriander
description: This deeply flavourful fish and cauliflower curry is like a golden sunset. Filled to the brim with bright veggies and tender gemfish
fillets, we reckon this beaming bowl will add the spice you never knew you needed to your night.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65a89a0e39e22d4840d70fbb-14371b92.jpeg
